chunk_content: CheckpointsWhen each training epoch completes a checkpoint is generated. A checkpoint is a fully functional version of a model which can both be deployed and used as the target model for subsequent fine-tuning jobs. Checkpoints can be particularly useful, as they can provide a snapshot of your model prior to overfitting having occurred. When a fine-tuning job completes you will have the three most recent versions of the model available to deploy.:::image type="content" source="../media/fine-tuning/checkpoints.png" alt-text="Screenshot of checkpoints UI." lightbox="../media/fine-tuning/checkpoints.png":::
